Package org.overture.parser.lex

Classes that implement the lexical analyser and its tokens.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BacktrackInputReader
    A class to allow arbitrary checkpoints and backtracking while parsing a file.
    DocStreamReader
    A class to read .doc encoded VDM files.
    DocxStreamReader
    A class to read an ODF encoded VDM file.
    LatexStreamReader
    A class to read LaTeX encoded VDM files.
    LexTokenReader
    The main lexical analyser class.
    ODFStreamReader
    A class to read an ODF encoded VDM file.
    XMLStreamReader
    A class to read an XML encoded VDM file, such as .docx or ODF
  • Enum Summary

    The different types of reader that may be obtained from a <BacktrackInputReader
  • Exception Summary

    An exception class for lexical analyser exceptions.
